    <title>download_kindle</title>
    <url>/2023/03/11/download-kindle/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Download-your-chinese-kindle"><a href="#Download-your-chinese-kindle" class="headerlink" title="Download your chinese kindle"></a>Download your chinese kindle</h1><h2 id="Kindle-download-helper"><a href="#Kindle-download-helper" class="headerlink" title="Kindle_download_helper"></a>Kindle_download_helper</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/yihong0618/Kindle_download_helper">Kindle_download_helper</a></p>
<p>主要步骤：</p>
<ul>
<li>pip3 install kindle_download </li>
<li>git clone <a href="https://github.com/yihong0618/Kindle_download_helper.git">https://github.com/yihong0618/Kindle_download_helper.git</a> &amp;&amp; cd Kindle_download_helper</li>
<li>pip3 install -r requirements.txt</li>
<li>python3 kindle.py  –dedrm –cn  ## –dedrm 移除 DRM</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
